Open localhost:8080
Sign in to Jenkins

- Manage jenkins
  - Plugins
     - Available plugins
        - Github integration 
        - Maven integration
        - Pileline:stage view
  - Credentials
     - system
        - Global credentials
            - Add credentials
                - Username & password (same as github username and password)
                - ID: jenkins-CICD
                - Click Create
  - Tools
     - Retain the default maven configuration
     - Add Java 
          - Name: JDK
          - JAVA_HOME: /usr/lib/jvm/java-11-openjdk-amd64
    - Add Git 
          - Name: Git
          - Path to git: /usr/bin/git
    - Add Gradle 
          - Name: Gradle
          - GRADLE_HOME: /usr/bin/gradle
    - Add Maven 
          - Name: Maven
          - MAVEN_HOME: /usr/bin/mvn
    - Apply & Save
